data.description: If you've been specifically looking for a home on the 5th green, 6th tee of Balboa Golf Course, then you've just hit the jackpot. This 3BD, 2BA home has a back deck waiting for you to perch on it and start your mornings sipping coffee and watching the Rainbird sprinkler system water the plants. If that's not your favorite way to relax, maybe the tub in the large master bathroom will suffice. Around the side is the golf cart storage, or your very own workshop. Come check out this property today to see everything it has to offer you! Agents see remarks.
